; mysak.fun — Cloudflare import zone file
; Generated: 2026-05-09
;
; HOW TO IMPORT:
;   Cloudflare Dashboard → mysak.fun → DNS → Import DNS Records → paste or upload this file
;
; NOTES:
;   - Cloudflare adds SOA/NS automatically; the ones below are skipped on import
;   - Proxied (orange-cloud) status is NOT in BIND format — set it manually after import:
;       penny      → DNS only (CNAME to Container Apps; Cloudflare can't proxy non-HTTP CNAME origins)
;       cloudfire  → Proxied (orange cloud)  ← App Service: mi-3-cloudfire-y29hf3, rg: mi-3-cloudfire-rg
;       aks-llm    → DNS only (direct A record, LB IP restricted to owner IP anyway)
;
$ORIGIN mysak.fun.
$TTL 300

; ── penny (Azure Container Apps — azure-penny) ───────────────────────────────
penny           300  IN  CNAME  ca-prd-eus-penny.thankfulisland-4131bb98.eastus.azurecontainerapps.io.
asuid.penny     300  IN  TXT    "24C4FD8D3A8507E43D386A411379665BC15579939C271A26E15AE5643A8A540A"

; ── aks-llm (AKS LLM cluster — az-llm-aks, pip-dev-wus2-llm) ────────────────
; Static IP survives nightly cluster destroy. Cluster dashboard at http://aks-llm.mysak.fun
aks-llm         300  IN  A      20.230.229.131

; ── cloudfire (Azure App Service — mi-3-cloudfire-rg) ───────────────────────
cloudfire       300  IN  CNAME  mi-3-cloudfire-y29hf3.azurewebsites.net.
asuid.cloudfire 300  IN  TXT    "24C4FD8D3A8507E43D386A411379665BC15579939C271A26E15AE5643A8A540A"
